description:
This is a 415 minute workout called 'Classic Rock Running Workout Playlist' from the channel Michael Daugherty.
The workout falls under Cardio/Running.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You won't need any equipmentThe workout has a The Rhythmic Powerhouse and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe means Beat-driven, strong but fluid, music-infused. This is especially good for When you want strength and rhythm to blend seamlessly. The The Endorphin Wave vibe means Elevated energy, feel-good movement, steady build. This is especially good for When you want a challenging but steady burn..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.
